Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.78,0:00:07.28,Cheerilee,,0,0,0,,I want to start our field trip here, in the world famous Canterlot Sculpture Garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.50,0:00:11.26,Cheerilee,,0,0,0,,That one over there represents friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.68,0:00:15.32,Cheerilee,,0,0,0,,All right, my little ponies!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.32,0:00:17.44,Cheerilee,,0,0,0,,This one represents victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.44,0:00:20.11,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,How cool would it be to have that for a cutie mark!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.11,0:00:21.66,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.97,0:00:25.12,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,If you were actually victoryful at somethin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.36,0:00:26.85,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,That's not a word!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.08,0:00:28.90,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,What are you? A dictionary?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.93,0:00:29.98,Cheerilee,,0,0,0,,Girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.19,0:00:33.62,Cheerilee,,0,0,0,,Now this is a really interesting statue.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.62,0:00:35.94,Cheerilee,,0,0,0,,What do you notice about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.27,0:00:37.72,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,It's got an eagle claw!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.72,0:00:39.04,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,And a lion paw!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.07,0:00:40.41,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,And a snake tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.64,0:00:43.19,Cheerilee,,0,0,0,,This creature is called a draconequus.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.19,0:00:46.93,Cheerilee,,0,0,0,,He has the head of a pony and a body made up of all sorts of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.93,0:00:49.03,Cheerilee,,0,0,0,,What do you suppose that represents?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.34,0:00:50.48,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Confusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.48,0:00:51.42,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.42,0:00:52.20,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Chaos!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.20,0:00:54.38,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,It's not chaos, you dodo!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.38,0:00:56.89,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Don't call me things I don't know the meaning of!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.89,0:00:58.78,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,And it is too chaos!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.78,0:00:59.64,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Is not!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.70,0:01:01.23,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,You're both wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.06,0:01:12.44,Cheerilee,,0,0,0,,Actually, in a way you're all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.41,0:01:15.49,Cheerilee,,0,0,0,,This statue represents discord…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.49,0:01:18.41,Cheerilee,,0,0,0,,…which means a lack of harmony between ponies.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.76,0:01:21.89,Cheerilee,,0,0,0,,In fact, you three have demonstrated discord so well…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.90,0:01:25.35,Cheerilee,,0,0,0,,…that you're each going to write me an essay explaining it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.38,0:01:28.12,Cheerilee,,0,0,0,,Now let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.44,0:01:29.96,Cheerilee,,0,0,0,,And I don't want any more fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.29,0:01:31.36,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,It's confusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.36,0:01:32.26,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.26,0:01:33.34,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Chaos!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.62,0:02:19.99,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Come back here, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.42,0:02:22.99,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.43,0:02:25.71,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Eeew! What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.64,0:02:30.43,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Cotton candy?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.16,0:02:38.05,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.12,0:02:40.04,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,It's not supposed to rain until tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.29,0:02:41.06,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,You can't just…!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.05,0:02:43.88,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,You did.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.62,0:02:49.68,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Hey! I didn't tell you to go anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.67,0:02:51.51,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Rainbow Dash!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.51,0:02:53.09,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,What's going on with that rain?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.09,0:02:54.33,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I mean… chocolate milk?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.33,0:02:56.00,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I mean… chocolate milk rain?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.40,0:02:58.70,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,There's crazy weather all over Equestria!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.90,0:03:01.69,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Cloudsdale's getting soaked by a major cola storm right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.93,0:03:05.42,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,But don't worry. I'm not leaving you till I get control of Ponyville.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.59,0:03:10.23,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Why would you wanna stop this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.14,0:03:17.30,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I heard about your troubles, Applejack, and I came to see if there's anything I could do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.39,0:03:18.26,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Without getting wet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.41,0:03:19.14,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Or dirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.44,0:03:20.83,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Or out from under my umbrella.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.04,0:03:31.08,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy! Do somethin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.13,0:03:33.48,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Now Angel, you really shouldn't…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.07,0:03:35.60,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,No! It's not possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.51,0:03:38.07,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I must be seeing things!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.82,0:03:40.90,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.09,0:03:43.66,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I've learned a new spell that'll fix everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.52,0:03:58.44,Twilight,,0,0,0,,My fail-safe spell…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.74,0:03:59.48,Twilight,,0,0,0,,…failed!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.60,0:04:00.67,Twilight,,0,0,0,,What do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.27,0:04:01.92,Spike,,0,0,0,,Uh… Give up?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.42,0:04:05.08,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Spike. Twilight will come up with something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.78,0:04:08.28,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Time for Plan B.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.57,0:04:11.71,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Rainbow! Can you corral all those clouds in one corner of the sky?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.92,0:04:22.63,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Applejack! I need you to bring those high-strung storm clouds down to earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.72,0:04:32.71,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Hey! What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.73,0:04:40.10,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Oh dear! I hope that none of the animals see these…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.10,0:04:43.02,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,…delicious chocolate-filled cotton candy clouds.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.02,0:04:45.28,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I'd hate to have to share them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.24,0:04:48.36,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,You and me both, sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.44,0:04:50.57,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.18,0:04:56.12,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,And when y'all are done with that, feel free to have some popcorn for dessert.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.35,0:04:57.19,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You see, Spike?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.19,0:04:58.82,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You should never give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.82,0:05:02.36,Twilight,,0,0,0,,There's nothing we can't overcome if we all work together.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.81,0:05:08.68,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Come on, girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.71,0:05:11.73,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Princess Celestia wants to see us all in Canterlot immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.93,0:05:21.91,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Princess Celestia!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.11,0:05:23.62,Twilight,,0,0,0,,We came as fast as we could.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.56,0:05:25.61,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.02,0:05:27.02,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Thank you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.13,0:05:28.02,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Is this about the weather?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.06,0:05:29.37,Twilight,,0,0,0,,And the animals' weird behavior?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.46,0:05:30.42,Twilight,,0,0,0,,What's happening out there?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.54,0:05:31.73,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Why isn't my magic working?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.83,0:05:32.34,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Is there…?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.11,0:05:34.32,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.32,0:05:37.37,Celestia,,0,0,0,,I've called you here for a matter of great importance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.60,0:05:39.17,Celestia,,0,0,0,,It seems an old foe of mine…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.63,0:05:42.91,Celestia,,0,0,0,,…someone I thought I had defeated long ago, has returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.25,0:05:46.10,Celestia,,0,0,0,,His name is Discord.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.27,0:05:50.31,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Discord is the mischievous spirit of disharmony.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.31,0:05:52.49,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Before my sister and I stood up to him…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.49,0:05:56.65,Celestia,,0,0,0,,…he ruled Equestria in an eternal state of unrest and unhappiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.65,0:06:02.02,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Luna and I saw how miserable life was for earth ponies… pegasi and unicorns alike.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.02,0:06:04.49,Celestia,,0,0,0,,So after discovering the Elements of Harmony…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.50,0:06:07.78,Celestia,,0,0,0,,…we combined our powers and rose up against him…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.78,0:06:09.47,Celestia,,0,0,0,,…turning him to stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.47,0:06:11.30,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Alright, Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.31,0:06:14.14,Celestia,,0,0,0,,I thought the spell we cast would keep him contained forever…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.14,0:06:17.02,Celestia,,0,0,0,,…but since Luna and I are no longer connected to the Elements…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.07,0:06:19.08,Celestia,,0,0,0,,…the spell has been broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.08,0:06:20.77,Twilight,,0,0,0,,No longer connected?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.77,0:06:24.75,Celestia,,0,0,0,,This is Canterlot tower, where the Elements are kept inside…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.75,0:06:26.67,Celestia,,0,0,0,,…since all of you recovered them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.04,0:06:31.66,Celestia,,0,0,0,,I need you to wield the Elements of Harmony once again and stop Discord…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.66,0:06:35.22,Celestia,,0,0,0,,…before he thrusts all of Equestria into eternal chaos.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.28,0:06:36.26,Twilight,,0,0,0,,But why us?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.51,0:06:37.15,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Why don't you…?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.18,0:06:37.71,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Hey, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.88,0:06:38.88,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,We're famous!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.13,0:06:41.77,Celestia,,0,0,0,,You six showed the full potential of the Elements…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.79,0:06:45.74,Celestia,,0,0,0,,…by harnessing the magic of your friendship to beat a mighty foe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.90,0:06:48.38,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Although Luna and I once wielded the Elements…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.38,0:06:50.78,Celestia,,0,0,0,,…it is you, who now control their power.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.78,0:06:53.56,Celestia,,0,0,0,,And it is you, who must defeat Discord!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.52,0:06:59.59,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Princess Celestia, you can count on…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.59,0:07:00.81,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Hold on a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.81,0:07:04.46,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Eternal chaos comes with chocolate rain, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.46,0:07:06.31,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Chocolate rain!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.63,0:07:08.33,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Don't listen to her, Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.49,0:07:10.89,Twilight,,0,0,0,,We'd be honored to use the Elements of Harmony again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.20,0:07:29.49,Rarity,,0,0,0,,You can keep the Elements. I'll take that case.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.73,0:07:31.12,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Have no fear, ponies.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.43,0:07:34.50,Celestia,,0,0,0,,I have total confidence that you will be able to defeat Discord…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.03,0:07:36.29,Celestia,,0,0,0,,…with these.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.26,0:07:43.66,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Oh well. If anyone needs me…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.74,0:07:47.92,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,…I'll be outside in the chocolate puddles with a giant swizzle straw.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.82,0:07:51.61,Twilight,,0,0,0,,The Elements! They're gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.78,0:07:55.15,Celestia,,0,0,0,,That chamber is protected by a powerful spell that only I can break.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.50,0:07:57.16,Celestia,,0,0,0,,This doesn't make sense…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.38,0:08:03.41,Discord,,0,0,0,,"Make sense"? Oh, what fun is there in making sense?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.48,0:08:05.46,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Discord! Show yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.90,0:08:11.48,Discord,,0,0,0,,Did you miss me, Celestia?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.36,0:08:14.51,Discord,,0,0,0,,I've missed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.31,0:08:19.24,Discord,,0,0,0,,It's quite lonely being encased in stone. But you wouldn't know that, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.26,0:08:22.82,Discord,,0,0,0,,Because I don't turn ponies into stone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.21,0:08:24.81,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.39,0:08:27.40,Celestia,,0,0,0,,What have you done with the Elements of Harmony?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.72,0:08:30.66,Discord,,0,0,0,,Oh, I just borrowed them for a teensy little while.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.58,0:08:35.67,Celestia,,0,0,0,,You'll never get away with this, Discord!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.23,0:08:38.90,Discord,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'd forgotten how grim you can be, Celestia.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.90,0:08:41.05,Discord,,0,0,0,,It's really quite boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.39,0:08:43.49,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Hey! Nopony insults the Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.06,0:08:49.57,Discord,,0,0,0,,You must be Rainbow Dash…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.60,0:08:52.91,Discord,,0,0,0,,…famed for her loyalty ‒ the Element of Harmony you represent.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.04,0:08:55.93,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,That's right! I'll always be loyal to the Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.41,0:08:58.03,Discord,,0,0,0,,We'll see about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.13,0:09:01.33,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I can't believe we're wasting our time talking to a tacky window.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.64,0:09:05.44,Discord,,0,0,0,,The beautiful Rarity, representing the Element of Generosity…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.47,0:09:07.12,Discord,,0,0,0,,…if I'm not mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.25,0:09:09.29,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,So you know who we are. Big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.28,0:09:12.77,Discord,,0,0,0,,Oh, I know much more than that, honest Applejack.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.81,0:09:14.74,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You seem to know our strengths too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.02,0:09:16.97,Discord,,0,0,0,,Yes, Twilight Sparkle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.04,0:09:20.90,Discord,,0,0,0,,And yours is the most powerful and elusive element ‒ magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.08,0:09:25.17,Discord,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy's is kindness and Pinkie Pie's is the personal favorite of mine…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.35,0:09:26.37,Discord,,0,0,0,,…laughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.48,0:09:28.10,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Pinkie!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.32,0:09:31.12,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,He's standing on your head!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.58,0:09:34.04,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Stop stalling, Discord!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.26,0:09:36.36,Celestia,,0,0,0,,What have you done with the Elements of Harmony?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.36,0:09:39.86,Discord,,0,0,0,,Oh! So boring, Celestia. Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.01,0:09:43.57,Discord,,0,0,0,,Fine. I'll tell you, but I'll only tell you my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.52,0:09:48.81,Discord,,0,0,0,,To retrieve your missing elements, just make sense of this change of events.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.17,0:09:52.22,Discord,,0,0,0,,Twists and turns are my master plan…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.37,0:09:55.49,Discord,,0,0,0,,…then find the Elements back where you began.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.53,0:09:59.02,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Can we go home now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.31,0:10:00.59,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,What do you reckon he meant?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.89,0:10:03.10,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,"Twists and turns" and then "back where we started".
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.45,0:10:04.88,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Twists and turns…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.18,0:10:06.54,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Twists and turns…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.77,0:10:09.42,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Twists and turns! That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.75,0:10:12.38,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I bet Discord hid the Elements in the palace labyrinth!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.18,0:10:14.81,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Good luck, my little ponies.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.19,0:10:18.42,Celestia,,0,0,0,,The fate of Equestria is in your hooves.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.50,0:10:20.85,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Princess. We won't let you down.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.21,0:10:30.72,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,We… We have to go in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.11,0:10:31.60,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Nope!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.96,0:10:34.60,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Dopey Discord forgot about these babies!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.99,0:10:37.93,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I'll just do a quick flyover and we'll have the Elements in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.19,0:10:43.47,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,My wings!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.13,0:10:46.89,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Your horn!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.13,0:10:46.89,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Your horn!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.16,0:10:47.96,Twilight,,0,0,0,,My horn!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.16,0:10:47.96,Rarity,,0,0,0,,My horn!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.63,0:11:01.00,Discord,,0,0,0,,You… You should see the looks on your faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.40,0:11:02.88,Discord,,0,0,0,,Priceless!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.11,0:11:05.70,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Give us our wings and horns back!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.84,0:11:07.34,Discord,,0,0,0,,You'll get them back in good time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.55,0:11:09.89,Discord,,0,0,0,,I simply took them to ensure there's no cheating.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.00,0:11:12.54,Discord,,0,0,0,,You see, this is the first rule of our game:
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.66,0:11:15.86,Discord,,0,0,0,,No flying and no magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.04,0:11:18.56,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,The first rule?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.90,0:11:22.76,Discord,,0,0,0,,The second rule is: everypony has to play or the game is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.89,0:11:24.58,Discord,,0,0,0,,And I win.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.27,0:11:27.91,Discord,,0,0,0,,Good luck, everypony!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.60,0:11:34.01,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Never fear, girls. We have each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.40,0:11:36.27,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Like Twilight said.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.50,0:11:39.80,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,There's nothing we can't overcome if we all stick together.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.44,0:11:42.99,Twilight,,0,0,0,,All right, girls! Let's do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.00,0:11:44.26,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Together!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.41,0:11:50.56,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Stay calm, girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.77,0:11:54.26,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Everypony head to the middle as fast as you can and we'll regroup there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.33,0:11:55.42,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Moving out!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.55,0:11:56.61,Rarity,,0,0,0,,See you in the center.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.89,0:11:58.69,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,See you guys there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.76,0:12:01.14,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.56,0:12:02.09,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Who's there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.20,0:12:03.73,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.60,0:12:19.61,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,What in tarnation?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.47,0:12:26.55,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.71,0:12:37.96,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Who are y'all?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.05,0:12:40.88,Somepony,,0,0,0,,The keepers of the grove of truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.98,0:12:42.68,Somepony,,0,0,0,,You may ask us…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.83,0:12:44.78,Somepony,,0,0,0,,…one question:
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.83,0:12:47.32,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Past, future or present.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.32,0:12:48.71,Somepony,,0,0,0,,But be warned…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.76,0:12:50.13,Somepony,,0,0,0,,…that the truth…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.34,0:12:52.75,Somepony,,0,0,0,,…may not always be pleasant.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.83,0:12:53.64,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Alright then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.09,0:12:56.15,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I don't trust this place for the hill a' beans…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.30,0:12:59.37,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,…but I got a real bad feelin' about this feller Discord.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.47,0:13:01.69,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,What's gonna come of this here mission we're on?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.21,0:13:07.29,Somepony,,0,0,0,,For the answer you seek…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.46,0:13:10.63,Somepony,,0,0,0,,…go ahead! Take a peek.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.31,0:13:15.44,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I hope I'll never see you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.44,0:13:16.56,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.69,0:13:17.59,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,-Fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.71,0:13:18.66,Rarity,,0,0,0,,-Fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.66,0:13:20.12,Twilight,,0,0,0,,It's settled then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.99,0:13:25.88,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.95,0:13:27.90,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Our friendship… over?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.14,0:13:34.56,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,It can't be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.93,0:13:36.83,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,It just can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.10,0:13:43.66,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,That just can't be the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.17,0:13:46.20,Somepony,,0,0,0,,When all the truth does…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.24,0:13:48.42,Somepony,,0,0,0,,…is make your heart ache…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.74,0:13:50.74,Somepony,,0,0,0,,…sometimes a lie
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.74,0:13:50.74,Discord,,0,0,0,,…sometimes a lie
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.99,0:13:52.55,Somepony,,0,0,0,,is easier to take.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.99,0:13:52.55,Discord,,0,0,0,,is easier to take.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.02,0:14:00.72,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Applejack! Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.82,0:14:02.45,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I thought I heard voices over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.09,0:14:04.44,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Who were you talking to?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.63,0:14:06.36,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I was talkin' to, uh…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.65,0:14:07.48,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Nopony!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.70,0:14:09.11,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Nopony whatsoever.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.20,0:14:11.98,Twilight,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.42,0:14:13.14,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Nothin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.55,0:14:15.30,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Come on. Uh, we best be goin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.71,0:14:17.93,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Did Applejack just…?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.82,0:14:19.95,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Come on, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.27,0:14:21.66,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Applejack wouldn't lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.33,0:14:37.80,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,This is the greatest balloon garden I've ever seen!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.20,0:14:41.29,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,It's the first balloon garden I've ever seen, but still…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.28,0:14:49.36,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,What gives?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.63,0:14:51.47,Discord,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Pinkie Pie?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.58,0:14:53.65,Discord,,0,0,0,,I thought you appreciated a good laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.72,0:14:54.73,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,It's different.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.04,0:14:56.48,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,They're laughing at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.60,0:14:58.60,Discord,,0,0,0,,It's hardly different.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.01,0:15:01.27,Discord,,0,0,0,,Your friends laugh at you all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.53,0:15:03.86,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,My friends laugh with me, not at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.99,0:15:05.39,Discord,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.25,0:15:13.82,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,No! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.02,0:15:23.61,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Stop laughing at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.00,0:15:27.14,Discord,,0,0,0,,Oh, poor Pinkie Pie.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.30,0:15:30.65,Discord,,0,0,0,,And here I thought laughter made you happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.79,0:15:33.84,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.15,0:15:36.81,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.57,0:15:43.13,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Pinkie Pie! Are we glad to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.17,0:15:44.82,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,You are, huh? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.07,0:15:46.29,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Need a good laugh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.78,0:15:47.48,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Pinkie?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.16,0:15:51.01,Twilight,,0,0,0,,What do you suppose has her so upset?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.12,0:15:52.18,Twilight,,0,0,0,,It's not like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.42,0:15:54.25,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I didn't notice anythin' strange about Pinkie.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.76,0:15:57.60,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.76,0:16:00.78,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Better pick up the pace before the stress of this gets the better of all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.33,0:16:09.35,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I was expecting an audience with the Princess, not outdoor sports.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.32,0:16:12.47,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Oh my.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.70,0:16:20.65,Discord,,0,0,0,,Welcome to your lucky day, Rarity.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.68,0:16:25.58,Discord,,0,0,0,,You've found the one thing in Equestria that could rival my face for sheer beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.43,0:16:29.74,Discord,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.87,0:16:30.87,Discord,,0,0,0,,You like?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.38,0:16:34.62,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Yes… I like very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.00,0:16:38.38,Rarity,,0,0,0,,No! No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.67,0:16:41.29,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I shan't succumb to such fabulousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.72,0:16:46.32,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Must… get to the center… to meet… the others…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.37,0:16:49.49,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.85,0:16:54.06,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Well, Rarity…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.67,0:16:56.57,Rarity,,0,0,0,,It took forever, but it was worth it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.00,0:17:03.73,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Who knew three little gemstones would turn out to be this handsome HUNK of a diamond?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.72,0:17:06.98,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Now to get you home.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.29,0:17:17.32,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Rarity! Are we glad to see…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.92,0:17:19.77,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Why are you carrying a humongous boulder?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.76,0:17:22.43,Rarity,,0,0,0,,What do you mean "boulder"?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.81,0:17:26.62,Rarity,,0,0,0,,This big, beautiful, bedazzling rock is a DIAMOND!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.08,0:17:28.85,Rarity,,0,0,0,,And it's all mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.91,0:17:31.06,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Keep your envious little eyes off it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.12,0:17:33.72,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I found it and it's mine, fair and square!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.42,0:17:47.42,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Okay, I can do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.62,0:17:48.21,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I can…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.85,0:17:51.57,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Oh! Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.81,0:17:52.67,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Butterflies?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.92,0:17:53.51,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.63,0:17:54.85,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Don't leave me here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.83,0:18:01.89,Discord,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.39,0:18:06.35,Discord,,0,0,0,,Looks like you've been left behind by your so-called friends, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.25,0:18:08.42,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.46,0:18:11.01,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I'm certain they're doing their best to find me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.41,0:18:15.74,Discord,,0,0,0,,Well, it must be so upsetting to know how weak and helpless they think you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.20,0:18:17.16,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.38,0:18:20.77,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I am weak and helpless and I appreciate their understanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.77,0:18:23.90,Discord,,0,0,0,,Yes, well… surely it burns you up, I mean…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.09,0:18:27.25,Discord,,0,0,0,,…that they're always pointing out your flaws, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.54,0:18:28.76,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Not really. In fact…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.98,0:18:33.64,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I think I'm awfully lucky to have friends who want me to be the best I can be.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.31,0:18:36.83,Discord,,0,0,0,,Oh, for goodness's sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.33,0:18:39.44,Discord,,0,0,0,,You've been kind for far too long, my dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.63,0:18:41.34,Discord,,0,0,0,,Time to be cruel!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.61,0:18:43.28,Discord,,0,0,0,,Arrivederci!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.25,0:18:49.46,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy! I'm so glad to see your friendly face.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.73,0:18:52.01,Twilight,,0,0,0,,This awful labyrinth is getting to everypony.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.99,0:18:56.02,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Oh, boo hoo hoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.29,0:19:00.66,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Why don't you wave your magic little horn and make everything all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.86,0:19:03.67,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right. You can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.81,0:19:05.09,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,You don't have one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.26,0:19:09.82,Twilight,,0,0,0,,What is happening to my friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.13,0:19:12.15,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,And what are YOU laughing at?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.46,0:19:13.50,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Chocolate milk!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.32,0:19:15.55,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Little help here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.44,0:19:18.51,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.00,0:19:19.64,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You're welcome…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.65,0:19:21.22,Rarity,,0,0,0,,But don't get any ideas about my gem!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.80,0:19:23.30,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I know where you live.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.80,0:19:36.09,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I've got you now, Element.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.04,0:19:44.92,Discord,,0,0,0,,I can see why you like these clouds so much. Very plush.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.37,0:19:46.57,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Get off there and put 'em up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.84,0:19:48.50,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,C'mon, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.56,0:19:51.36,Discord,,0,0,0,,Hey, I'm here to deliver a message.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.41,0:19:53.28,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I've got a message for you too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.31,0:19:55.76,Discord,,0,0,0,,Listen closely. This is important.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.25,0:19:57.87,Discord,,0,0,0,,A weighty choice is yours to make,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.93,0:19:59.89,Discord,,0,0,0,,The right selection or a big mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.35,0:20:02.26,Discord,,0,0,0,,If a wrong choice you choose to pursue,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.26,0:20:05.85,Discord,,0,0,0,,The foundations of home will crumble without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.95,0:20:11.04,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Cloudsdale?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.57,0:20:12.44,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Crumble…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.72,0:20:13.84,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,without me…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.36,0:20:16.49,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,NO!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.17,0:20:19.78,Discord,,0,0,0,,That box contains your wings.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.84,0:20:21.38,Discord,,0,0,0,,You can take them and leave the game…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.40,0:20:25.08,Discord,,0,0,0,,…or you can carry on aimlessly wandering this maze.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.10,0:20:26.02,Discord,,0,0,0,,Your choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.69,0:20:36.03,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Must… find… Rainbow Dash…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.74,0:20:40.25,Twilight,,0,0,0,,As a team… we're unstoppable.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.86,0:20:43.61,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Rainbow Dash won't let us down.
